name: 10 minutes wasted
description:
My GameJam Entry for the Ms.Paint GameJam.

All art asset and code was made by me on paint and on unity. Thank you to some friends that helped me make some Audio bites. 

Music was done by David Malenfant.

Might have to make a sound update since there is none when a enemy is hit atm.

If I ever update this game, you can still download the GameJam version.
